Package: ICERglossary
Title: JSON-based glossary for multilingual LSA reporting
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R:
    person("Martin", "Verner", , "martin.verner@unibe.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a JSON-based glossary and lookup utilities for consistent,
    multilingual wording in large-scale assessment reporting. The package is
    designed to support Quarto-based reports, plots, and dynamically generated
    text elements, but can also be used as a standalone glossary lookup tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    jsonlite
